channel.title: Well this title should change, Tol Royal quiz (jk it is not a real quiz)
channel.description:
If you're a noble what would you pick to carry in your royal bag?
[poll type=regular] * GOLD * GEMS * NOTHING [/poll]
Correct answer is GOLD!
If you're a princess would you sleep in a dark pink fancy double bed?
[poll name=poll2 type=regular public=true] * Yup * Nope [/poll]
If you said Yup you are correct
If you are a king would you be a psycho, evil, good, or neut king
[poll name=poll3 type=regular public=true] * Psycho * EVUL * Goody * Neuty [/poll]
If you said Any one of them you're correct
If you are a drunk would be you rather be drunk or drink coffee
[poll name=poll4 type=regular] * IMMA DRUNK * #Coffeeforlife [/poll]
If you said IMMA DRUNK you're correct
BTW this is just a joke don't take it seriously
